text: Play Misty for Me is a 1971 American psychological thriller movie directed by first time director Clint Eastwood (who also stars) and also starring Jessica Walter, Donna Mills, John Larch, Irene Hervey, Clarice Taylor, Don Siegel. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1971 thriller movies Category:American thriller movies Category:Movies directed by Clint Eastwood
title: Play Misty for Me
